            },
            "answer_text": "What is a global environment? The global environment is essentially the larger external environment around you, but generally beyond your current physical reach. For a business in Vietnam, the city, and possibly the province you are in, will immediately be your local environment. Vietnam, as a marketplace in your country, will be your national environment. The world out there beyond the geographical borders of your country will be your global environment, especially in terms of political/monetary/market/competition/technological dynamics which may directly or indirectly influence what you are thinking and doing. ",
